# SumDroid Android Build Workflow

sumdroid-android-build is an automated CI/CD workflow to build Android APK files using Gradlew. 
It supports custom build arguments, artifact generation, and Slack notifications for build status.

## Features
- Automated APK build
- Gradlew arguments support
- Artifact generation
- Slack notifications

## How to Use
1. Clone this repository
2. Configure inputs (SERVICE_LOCATION, ANDROID_LOCATION, BUILD_ARTIFACT)
3. Set your secrets (SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL)
4. Trigger the workflow via push, release, or pull request

